snippet.title: Yesterday's News - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Craft hilarious headlines with your friends in this 3-8 player party game. Score points by composing the wittiest headlines or by supplying the perfect words for your friends' creations!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2850560/Yesterdays_News/
